Class QClass.QObject

java.lang.Object
qlang.core.lang.Q.QClass.QObject
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cloneable
Enclosing class:
QClass
public static class QClass.QObject extends Object implements Cloneable
This class represents an instance of a QObject, used for objects created from QClasses.
